{"tid":632666,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警署後門查問　警長：保事主私隱","createTime":"2018-04-17T15:11:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T15:35:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3f88304f523b5eaa299e42dbf01d873fa2cb6035","tid":632666,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T15:11:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180417/20363684?_ga=2.108777346.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180417%2F20363684%3F_ga%3D2.108777346.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=kJKF5bKJ3bb1eMIg7r1iL4M9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=4b91aa01\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180417%2F20363684%3F_ga%3D2.108777346.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=d46eb152\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180417/20363684?_ga=2.108777346.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n警署後門查問　警長：保事主私隱<br />\n<br />\n4.9K<br />\n法庭<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180417/large/17ls3p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180417%2Flarge%2F17ls3p4.jpg&h=2273e083&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【勒索「罰款」案】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】休班警長涉指控男乘客非禮，勒索1萬元以換「放生」對方，案件昨續審。法官裁定案件表面證供成立後，警長出庭自辯，他稱當天雖休班，但見男乘客緊盯女士臀部，於是截查，「休班同當值冇分別，見到可疑人就去處理」；又稱因不想路人聽到事主「私隱」，為免對方尷尬，遂到警署後門查問。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n裁定表證成立<br />\n<br />\n辯方昨一度申請毋須答辯，稱被告張偉基（49歲，圖）與男事主X有協議，X願付律師費以保障被告日後可能因放走他而惹麻煩要找律師；X自願付1萬元，表示他遵守協議，被告沒不當要求。法官反駁，男乘客指警長威脅揚開醜事「到時你冇前途㗎喇」已是恫嚇，法官裁定表證成立。<br />\n<br />\n被告出庭自辯稱1986年加入警隊，案發7月13日，被告從金鐘下班乘港鐵，見X不停注視路經女士的臀部，於是監視並跟蹤X。被告指X在太子站下車並在月台逗留，他遂上前截查。X起初質疑他身份，他遂表示「上面就係我哋差館」，可核實身份。當二人走到警署附近，X突然稱怕麻煩不想到警署，願相信被告身份。由於彌敦道人多「望住晒我哋」，為了保障X「私隱」，他遂往警署後門續查問。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC1116/17<br />\n■記者歐陽聯發"},{"pid":"ba5059d9ee975e44b9d8660243dc4186b3b76f83","tid":632666,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T15:23:05.000Z","msg":"硬膠泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3124d977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff15f2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=27225035&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ebed7ef2f47d93c081548e79bb6e222220e0d25f","tid":632666,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T15:35:20.000Z","msg":"眼神係無得證實，一個人望向一個方向唔代表佢係望緊一樣嘢㗎喎"}]}